data.description: Perfect island retreat at The Point in Emerald Isle!  Well maintained and updated over the years by original owner.  Private wooded .292 acre lot features amazing live oak trees and complete privacy behind the house. Short walk to the ocean and The Point to enjoy amazing sunsets and wide, natural beaches. Full covered front porch with plenty of room for rocking chairs and a full screened-in back porch to enjoy your privacy and enjoy outdoor dining.  Open concept main level with living, dining and kitchen.  Three large bedrooms and additional office/room and two full baths complete the first level.  Second level 22x18 bonus room with wet bar, and full wrap around decking for grand vista views and entertaining. Ground level includes 2 storage areas,  covered parking under the house for 2 vehicles along with gathering areas to entertain or just relax.  Emerald Isle bike path is right around the corner. Home has never been a rental would make a perfect Airbnb & VRBO with office having a closet and bonus room for extra guest.
